<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1385807-i-read-many-of-his-books-between-the-age">I read many of his books between the age of 10 and 20. I thought I would re-read some. Having just been to French Polynesia I started reading Tales of the South Pacific. Boy, times have changed: I could not finish this book because it was rife with colonial attitudes and blatant racism. I am wondering if this book will be the same? Thoughts????</a>
</div>
