        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer79691491" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11440143845020248338">I know some consider Michener a lightweight - in fact I don&apos;t know anyone else who enjoys reading him - but I have enjoyed learning a bit more about complicated social histories of a particular area. Piecing together the history of the Xhosa, Zulu and other natives in southern African, as well as the Dutdh and English colonisers was very interesting to me. I am more inclined to read such a book with human stories (if fictitious), than to pick up a non-fiction on the history of So. Africa. Anyone</span>
  <span id="freeText11440143845020248338" style="display:none">I know some consider Michener a lightweight - in fact I don't know anyone else who enjoys reading him - but I have enjoyed learning a bit more about complicated social histories of a particular area. Piecing together the history of the Xhosa, Zulu and other natives in southern African, as well as the Dutdh and English colonisers was very interesting to me. I am more inclined to read such a book with human stories (if fictitious), than to pick up a non-fiction on the history of So. Africa. Anyone else out there enjoy Michener?</span>
  <a data-text-id="11440143845020248338" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
